## Dashboard Creation Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define stakeholders: Who will use this dashboard and why?
- [ ] 2. Define KPIs: What metrics matter most to each stakeholder?
- [ ] 3. Map data sources: Where does each metric come from?
- [ ] 4. Design layout: What goes on the overview vs. detail views?
- [ ] 5. Build the dashboard: Connect data sources and build visualizations
- [ ] 6. Add context: Labels, benchmarks, targets, and trend lines
- [ ] 7. Test with users: Does it answer the questions stakeholders have?
- [ ] 8. Set refresh cadence: How often is data updated?

## Key Inputs
- Dashboard purpose: {{dashboard_purpose}}
- Stakeholders: {{stakeholders}}
- KPIs needed: {{kpis}}
- Data sources: {{data_sources}}
- Tools available: {{tools}}
